            "body": "<pre><code>(.)\\1{2}\n<\/code><\/pre>\n\n<p>(.) matches any char<\/p>\n\n<p>\\1 matches that exactly char <\/p>\n\n<p>{2} is to grant its 2 more of that<\/p>\n",
